Spec: Shared Constants
Purpose:
  Provide shared values for SpecDD paths, release metadata, URLs, version parsing, and common CLI text.

Structure:
  constants.ts: Shared constants implementation.

Owns:
  constants.ts

Can modify:
  constants.ts

Must:
  Define SpecDD file and directory paths used across commands and services.
  Define public SpecDD help and changelog URLs used in CLI output.
  Define GitHub release API coordinates used for distribution lookup.
  Define distribution asset names used for release downloads.
  Define version parsing patterns shared by services.
  Define common CLI footer text shared by command help output.
  Keep values static and free of runtime side effects.

Must not:
  Read environment variables.
  Perform filesystem or network operations.

Exposes:
  SpecDD path constants
  SpecDD URL constants
  distribution asset constants
  version parsing constants
  CLI text constants
